name: Analog Surf (Music Video)
description:
With this drop I deliver my first crypto collection (analog surf) and finish the first cycle of my nft journey. 

Extracts from surf videos processed by 90s analog video gear and contemporary glitch boxes. 

Music mixed and produced using Ableton, Giannini Super Sonic guitar, effects pedals (reverb hall of fame, blues driver and dd7), V-Station VST plugins for synths and shure sm57 mic plugged in a mk3 pre amp to a focusrite 2i4 audio interface. 

.mp4 // 800x600px
